00:00:31.850 --> 00:00:34.080
intuitively makes
a lot of sense.

00:00:34.080 --> 00:00:38.180
You guys are great at
addressing problems,

00:00:38.180 --> 00:00:41.620
and I want to talk to
you about a problem

00:00:41.620 --> 00:00:44.804
