00:15:28.010 --> 00:15:30.480
I'm like, dude, that's
not a very good idea.

00:15:30.480 --> 00:15:32.910
So part of what I do
is encouraging people

00:15:32.910 --> 00:15:35.800
to do smart things
in a smart way.

