morbidity study in 2000

00:15:44.190 --> 00:15:46.340
looking at what gets
people sick and ill.

00:15:46.340 --> 00:15:48.280
And people think, oh,
it's just my genetics.

00:15:48.280 --> 00:15:50.890
Genetics are about 20%
of their conclusion.

00:15:50.890 --> 00:15:53.990
The biggest factor was basically
exercise, smoking, and diet,

00:15:53.990 --> 00:15:58.539
which are the big factors which
seem to affect how people-- I'm

00:15:58.539 --> 00:15:59.830
just going to say it right now.

