00:16:14.210 --> 00:16:16.410
a ton of sense from
this equation of what

00:16:16.410 --> 00:16:19.180
are some things to
start to think about,

00:16:19.180 --> 00:16:21.470
particularly because
of the following thing.

00:16:21.470 --> 00:16:25.660
If you were inactive in your 60s
in this red line on the left,

00:16:25.660 --> 00:16:27.790
you have a higher
chance of dying

00:16:27.790 --> 00:16:30.882
than if you're very
