00:16:34.631 --> 00:16:37.460
So basically the important
thing about all this

00:16:37.460 --> 00:16:39.720
is that we want
people to be active,

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:42.127
and we want to in our
health care system

00:16:42.127 --> 00:16:43.710
keep them out of
this kind of end zone

00:16:43.710 --> 00:16:45.480
where they're having
a really tough time.

00:16:45.480 --> 00:16:47.563
We want to keep them active
until the last-- I had

00:16:47.563 --> 00:16:49.870
an 82-year-old lady run
