body, tip to toe.

00:25:21.720 --> 00:25:25.050
And for a kinetic chain to
work, it needs to be flexible

00:25:25.050 --> 00:25:26.240
and it needs to be strong.

00:25:26.240 --> 00:25:29.120
So if you come in to see me with
an achy knee or an achy shin

00:25:29.120 --> 00:25:32.030
