00:25:35.860 --> 00:25:37.860
If you have some arthritis
in your knee, you do.

00:25:37.860 --> 00:25:39.950
If you have a
herniated disc, you do.

00:25:39.950 --> 00:25:41.680
But if you make your
kinetic chain more

00:25:41.680 --> 00:25:45.030
effective through strength
training and flexibility,

00:25:45.030 --> 00:25:47.640
those things are going
to feel a ton better.

