So whatever it is, if it's
gentle stretching, a swim,

00:30:07.885 --> 00:30:12.350
a yoga class, or maybe nothing,
but I think basically doing

00:30:12.350 --> 00:30:15.910
something daily just helps for
a number of different reasons.

00:30:15.910 --> 00:30:17.660
Obviously you don't
need the reinforcement

00:30:17.660 --> 00:30:20.270
because your lifestyle behaviors
are already deeply entrenched

00:30:20.270 --> 00:30:24.400
with exercise, but I think
doing something every day,

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:28.250
physiologically, mentally is
most helpful for most people.

00:30:28.250 --> 00:30:31.050
